2002-04-24 Johannes Schmid <clubfan@users.sourceforge.net>

	Reviewed by Naba Kumar <kh_naba@users.sourceforge.net>
	
	* src/appwiz_page1.c, src/appwizard_cbs.c, src/glades.c, 
