2002-03-10  Stephane Demurget  <demurgets@free.fr>

	Fix for #525107.

	* src/anjuta_cbs.c: (on_open_filesel_ok_clicked): removed unecessary
	  calls to fileselection_hide_widget,
	  (on_open_filesel_cancel_clicked): removed.

