	  Changed shortcut for Find/Replace to CTRL+SHIFT+F (to
	  reflect the opposite of Find (CTRL+F) and also to leave
	  CTRL+R or Redo.
	  
	  Changed Glade summon with ALT+G, which frees the ATL+E
	  for poping up the edit menu.
	  
